	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64632881"><p>Highly advanced AI is not needed on 90% of PC unless it&rsquo;s mining your behavior for someone else to use. Your PC already has enough AI power to be useful for personal things (voice recognition, media classification, etc.). Note I said 90%, there are about 10% of users who may need local AI capabilities because they are doing video production or something like that. Though even that&rsquo;s iffy (why not push that out to the cloud?).</p></div>
